snippet.title: Amber Heard Alleges Abuse Johnny Depp.
snippet.description:
Johnny Deep Amber Heard Filed a domestic violence restraining order against husband Johnny Deep, Claiming He physically assulted her.

Heard allegedly brought photographic evidence of the alleged abuse she suffered. 

Heard Allegedly appeared in court Friday, May 27, with a bruise on her face. 

"Johnny will not respond to any of the salacious false stories, gossip, misinformation and lies about his personal life."

"Hopefully the dissolution of this short marriage will be resolved quickly. 

It was reported that Deep's family does not like heard, creating friction in their relationship.

Deep was previously partnered with Venessa Paradis for 14 Years. They have 2 children together.
